snippet.title: Associated Press
snippet.description:
Since 1846, The Associated Press has done more than any organization in the world to expand the reach of factual reporting.

For the latest in-depth coverage on today's breaking news including top stories, international, politics, lifestyle, business, entertainment and more visit https://apnews.com.
